Method Detail

mapRow

T mapRow(QueryResultIF result,
         int rowno)
EXPERIMENTAL: This method is called once for each row in query results, and the returned object is added to the list returned by queryForList.

Parameters:
result - the query result object
rowno - the number of this row in the current query result (in zero-based counting)
Returns:
an object to put into the query result list
